<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 01:08:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>帕累托最优性揭示了细胞原型图集</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pareto-optimality-reveals-an-atlas-of-cellular-archetypes</link><description>这种模式是帕累托最优性的标志，帕累托最优性是一个数学概念，描述相互竞争的目标如何创建最优解决方案的“前沿”。正如你无法在不妥协的情况下制造出一辆速度最快且燃油效率最高的汽车一样，细胞也无法同时优化所有生物功能。细胞可能专门从事能量生产、防御或生长，但很少同时擅长这三项。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pareto-optimality-reveals-an-atlas-of-cellular-archetypes2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 01:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pareto-optimality-reveals-an-atlas-of-cellular-archetypes</guid></item><item><title>将双层衣服加倍，摇匀，打破一个，并保持另一个完好无损：欢迎，黑暗标量！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/double-the-doublet-shake-well-break-one-and-keep-the-other-intact-welcome-dark-scalars</link><description>搜索还没有结束——高亮度大型强子对撞机和拟议的未来圆形对撞机（FCC）的未来运行将继续寻找这些“惰性”双胞胎，看看它们是否隐藏在更高的能量水平。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/double-the-doublet-shake-well-break-one-and-keep-the-other-intact-welcome-dark-scalars.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:53:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/double-the-doublet-shake-well-break-one-and-keep-the-other-intact-welcome-dark-scalars</guid></item><item><title>PARG 抑制可通过 Hippo 途径阻止胆管癌的进展，并增强对化疗和免疫治疗的反应</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/parg-inhibition-halts-cholangiocarcinoma-progression-via-the-hippo-pathway-and-enhances-response-to-chemotherapy-and-immunotherapy</link><description>PARG 抑制增强了小鼠胆管细胞癌模型中化疗和 PD-1 阻断的疗效。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/parg-inhibition-halts-cholangiocarcinoma-progression-via-the-hippo-pathway-and-enhances-response-to-chemotherapy-and-immunotherapy2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/parg-inhibition-halts-cholangiocarcinoma-progression-via-the-hippo-pathway-and-enhances-response-to-chemotherapy-and-immunotherapy</guid></item><item><title>殖民褐矮星——失败恒星周围的生命</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/colonizing-brown-dwarfs-life-around-failed-stars</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/colonizing-brown-dwarfs-life-around-failed-stars</guid></item><item><title>唐氏综合症阿尔茨海默病病理学的生物学和临床分期</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/biological-and-clinical-staging-of-alzheimer-disease-pathology-in-down-syndrome</link><description>在患有唐氏综合症的成年人中，阿尔茨海默病的临床和生物学分期与散发病例相比表现出更大的一致性，支持使用基于认知的分期进行临床试验登记。大多数不一致的病例表现出比临床阶段更先进的病理学，突出了该人群的恢复机制。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/biological-and-clinical-staging-of-alzheimer-disease-pathology-in-down-syndrome.png" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/biological-and-clinical-staging-of-alzheimer-disease-pathology-in-down-syndrome</guid></item><item><title>ACSL4 相关的脂质代谢是 KMT2A 重排急性髓系白血病的独特治疗脆弱性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/acsl4-associated-lipid-metabolism-is-a-distinct-therapeutic-vulnerability-in-kmt2a-rearranged-acute-myeloid-leukemia</link><description>谢弗等人。将 ACSL4 识别为 KMT2A 重排 AML 中的选择性漏洞。 ACSL4 敲低损害白血病生长&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/acsl4-associated-lipid-metabolism-is-a-distinct-therapeutic-vulnerability-in-kmt2a-rearranged-acute-myeloid-leukemia2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 23:53:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/acsl4-associated-lipid-metabolism-is-a-distinct-therapeutic-vulnerability-in-kmt2a-rearranged-acute-myeloid-leukemia</guid></item><item><title>维生素 C 抑制 ACSL4 以减轻灵长类动物的铁衰老</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/vitamin-c-inhibits-acsl4-to-alleviate-ferro-aging-in-primates</link><description>刘等人。确定铁触发的老化途径（称为铁老化）是由 ACSL4 精心策划的。维生素 C 直接靶向并抑制 ACSL4，从而阻止铁老化。他们的进一步研究表明，非人类灵长类动物的长期补充可以系统性地延缓衰老并改善代谢和神经功能。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/vitamin-c-inhibits-acsl4-to-alleviate-ferro-aging-in-primates.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 23:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/vitamin-c-inhibits-acsl4-to-alleviate-ferro-aging-in-primates</guid></item><item><title>具有最大偶极矩的分子不是由于电负性差异造成的</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/molecules-with-largest-dipole-moments-arent-due-to-electronegativity-differences</link><description>计算分析挑战鲍林的极性观点&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/molecules-with-largest-dipole-moments-arent-due-to-electronegativity-differences.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 23:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/molecules-with-largest-dipole-moments-arent-due-to-electronegativity-differences</guid></item><item><title>通往杏仁核的直接听觉皮层下路径与人类的恐惧相关</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-direct-auditory-subcortical-route-to-the-amygdala-associated-with-fear-in-humans</link><description>Kosteletou-Kassotaki 等人在 JNeurosci 上发表的新文章：通过丘脑 MGB 连接下丘和基底外侧杏仁核的白质束与人们更好的听力和更高的自我报告恐惧感有关。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-direct-auditory-subcortical-route-to-the-amygdala-associated-with-fear-in-humans2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 23:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-direct-auditory-subcortical-route-to-the-amygdala-associated-with-fear-in-humans</guid></item><item><title>单细胞分析确定 RETN+ 单核细胞来源的抵抗素作为乙型肝炎病毒相关慢性慢加急性肝衰竭的治疗靶点</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/single-cell-analysis-identifies-retn-monocyte-derived-resistin-as-a-therapeutic-target-in-hepatitis-b-virus-related-acute-on-chronic-liver-failure</link><description>GUTImage 来自 Xu 等人题为“GUT”的论文。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/single-cell-analysis-identifies-retn-monocyte-derived-resistin-as-a-therapeutic-target-in-hepatitis-b-virus-related-acute-on-chronic-liver-failure.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 22:53:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/single-cell-analysis-identifies-retn-monocyte-derived-resistin-as-a-therapeutic-target-in-hepatitis-b-virus-related-acute-on-chronic-liver-failure</guid></item></channel></rss>